    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable budget-friendly option. While the engine and transmission are functional, there are noticeable cosmetic imperfections including some paint fading and minor dents on the exterior. The interior shows signs of significant use with some wear on the upholstery, and it may require some upcoming maintenance for optimal performance. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable work vehicle or a first car at a reasonable price point.",
