    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable companion that\u2019s ready for any adventure! This vehicle is a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a solid, functional ride with plenty of personality. While it shows some honest signs of its travels and typical wear, it runs well and offers great value for those who prioritize practicality and dependability. It\u2019s a hardworking car that still has many miles left to give!",
