    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or parts car. The engine currently suffers from a heavy oil leak and a persistent knocking noise that suggests internal wear, while the transmission is slipping and struggles to engage gears properly. Additionally, the body shows signs of significant rust and the interior requires a deep cleaning and several repairs. It is sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed.",
